  • Constructor Details

    • Order

      public Order(Date timeStamp, Staff waiter, List<MenuItem> orderItems, List<Promotion> promotionItems, Customer customer, Table table)
      Create a new order according to the table number and customer. An order must have aleast an a le carte item or promotion set.
      Parameters:
      timeStamp - This is the time when the order is made.
      waiter - This is the waiter who made the order.
      orderItems - This is a list of a le carte items ordered.
      promotionItems - This is a list of promotion set ordered.
      customer - This is the customer who made the order.
      table - This is the table where the customer is sitting.
